title: Cats the musical
description:
Cats, the longest-running musical in Broadway history, the show that changed the face of modern musicals - now as you've never seen it beforeâ€¦ and as you'll never see it again! The ultimate home video version of the Olivier and Tony Award-winning classic boasts an all-star cast headed by Elaine Paige (London's original Grizabella) and Sir John Mills, with music performed by an eighty-piece orchestra. From the opening dance number to the final refrain of Memory, you'll want to experience Cats - Now and Forever! 

DVD rip 1998 London cast at Adelphi theatre

Andrew Lloyd Webber, Cameron Mackintosh, Trevor Nunn, Gillian Lynne, John Napier and Gerry Schoenfeld
